erjang.driver.efile
Class EFile

java.lang.Object
  erjang.driver.EDriverControl
      erjang.driver.EDriverInstance
          erjang.driver.efile.EFile

public class EFile
extends EDriverInstance

Java does nor support proper non-blocking IO for files (i.e., you cannot select on a file). Select is only supported for sockets (and server sockets).
